    "client_msg_id": "f269c3e0-69e0-4d26-8c9c-ffd9fed290c3",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "The \"query API\" is is just a bunch of methods `filter` and `props`. With these source triples:\n``` :me\n  rdf:type schema:Person;\n  schema:name \"Emmanuel Oga\";\n  schema:familyName \"Oga\";\n  schema:givenName \"Emmanuel\";\n  schema:jobTitle \"Software Engineer\";\n  schema:knowsLanguage \"en-US\", \"es-ES\".```\nI can find my name like this:\n```val name = qs.filter(s = \":me\").props(\"schema:name\") // -&gt; returns \"Emmanuel Oga\"```",
    "user": "UN9SCH5RD",
    "ts": "1611480536.005200",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "user_profile": {
      "avatar_hash": "gaa31b79aded",
      "image_72": "https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/aa31b79adedc3f60547769f1a8971ba6.jpg?s=72&d=https%3A%2F%2Fa.slack-edge.com%2Fdf10d%2Fimg%2Favatars%2Fava_0015-72.png",
      "first_name": "",
      "real_name": "Emmanuel Oga",
      "display_name": "Emmanuel Oga",
      "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
      "name": "emmanueloga",
      "is_restricted": false,
      "is_ultra_restricted": false
    },
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "rich_text",
        "block_id": "YMkA",
        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "The \"query API\" is is just a bunch of methods "
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "filter",
                "style": {
                  "code": true
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " and "
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "props",
                "style": {
                  "code": true
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": ". With these source triples:\n"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "rich_text_preformatted",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " :me\n  rdf:type schema:Person;\n  schema:name \"Emmanuel Oga\";\n  schema:familyName \"Oga\";\n  schema:givenName \"Emmanuel\";\n  schema:jobTitle \"Software Engineer\";\n  schema:knowsLanguage \"en-US\", \"es-ES\"."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "I can find my name like this:\n"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "rich_text_preformatted",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "val name = qs.filter(s = \":me\").props(\"schema:name\") // -> returns \"Emmanuel Oga\""
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
